														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1243036">
									

<p>On that note, I live in the suburbs, so I have access to a sewage system that takes the waste far, far away from me. The concept of a septic tank has always creeped me out, because it's a giant concrete box buried underground and you have no way of knowing what's inside it, and your refuse stays there forever (forever [FOR-E-VER]), just festering&#8230;</p>
<p>Maybe I should make an SCP what lives in septic tanks, or is a septic tank, or whatever. Anything with septic tanks. *shudders*</p>
<p>Oh, and this is a great story.</p>

